author: Warhammer
description:
Type like your life depends on it in Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun – Words of Vengeance!

Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun - Words of Vengeance is a creative twist on epic boomer shooter Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun. Instead of mowing down your enemies with elite FPS skills, kill the relentless hordes of enemies that descend upon you by typing out words.

Obliterate your enemies by quickly typing their death sentences but beware as one typo could spell your own demise.  
Play for Free now on Steam!

author: Warhammer
description:
Obliterate heretics in the name of the Emperor in Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun 2!

Following directly on from the end of Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun, your duty takes you to new locations in a branching, single-player campaign that effortlessly blends the grimdark Warhammer 40:000 universe with a fast-paced first-person shooter.

This is just the beginning! We have even more exciting news to share about Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun 2 so make sure to wishlist the game and follow our Steam page, so you don’t miss out on any of the upcoming announcements.

Warhammer 40,000 Boltgun 2 is coming to PC, PS5 & Xbox Series X|S in 2026.
